    $( Part 2 of the Riesz representation theorem for bounded linear
       functionals.  The value of a bounded linear functional corresponds to a
       unique inner product.  Part of Theorem 17.3 of [Halmos] p. 31.  For part
       1, see ~ riesz1 . $)
